OL,3,CJersey minister to look into
OL,4,Coverturning homosexuality convictions
OL,6,F"I think it is right and proper that
OL,7,Fan apology should be made for
OL,8,Fcriminalising people in these sorts of
OL,9,Fcircumstances."
OL,11,FDeputy Tom Coles had raised the issue
OL,12,Fin the States Assembly, calling the
OL,13,Fcurrent situation "immoral".
OL,15,FHe explains: "We still have people
OL,16,Fpunished for a crime which is no
OL,17,Flonger a crime and it's immoral to
OL,18,Fhave that conviction there.
